OL,3,CPost Office involved in 'possible
OL,4,Ccriminal conspiracy', investigator says
OL,6,FThe Post Office 'didn't want to
OL,7,Fcommission a review' into faulty
OL,8,FHorizon IT software, according to
OL,9,Finvestigators. ITV News Correspondent
OL,10,FGeraint Vincent reports.
OL,12,FThe Post Office has been accused of
OL,13,Fbeing involved in a possible "criminal
OL,14,Fconspiracy" by an independent
OL,15,Finvestigator who played a pivotal role
OL,16,Fin uncovering the Horizon IT scandal.
