OL,3,CPost Office involved in 'possible
OL,4,Ccriminal conspiracy', investigator says
OL,6,FIan Henderson, who in 2012 alongside
OL,7,FRon Warmington was hired from Second
OL,8,FSight and asked to investigate
OL,9,Fpotential issues with the software,
OL,10,Fgave evidence at the Post Office
OL,11,Finquiry on Tuesday.
OL,13,FMr Henderson told the inquiry that he
OL,14,Ffelt former Post Office boss Paula
OL,15,FVennells "frequently and consistently"
OL,16,Ftried to steer him away from probing
OL,17,Fmiscarriages of justice.
