OL,3,CPost Office involved in 'possible
OL,4,Ccriminal conspiracy', investigator says
OL,6,FThe inquiry was told his colleague,
OL,7,FRon Warmington, had spoken to sub-
OL,8,Fpostmaster Alun Jones and told him the
OL,9,Factions of The Post Office had been
OL,10,F"the worst corporate behaviour I've
OL,11,Fever come across".
OL,13,FIn his witness statement to the probe,
OL,14,FMr Warmington said: "I was very used
OL,15,Fto dealing with conflict in my
OL,16,Fprofession but had never encountered
OL,17,Fsuch ferocious resistance to almost
OL,18,Fevery sentence used in every report.
