OL,3,CPost Office involved in 'possible
OL,4,Ccriminal conspiracy', investigator says
OL,6,FSecond Sight studied over 140 sub-
OL,7,Fpostmasters' claims and produced a
OL,8,Freport in 2013 finding that the
OL,9,FHorizon system was largely "flawed"
OL,10,Fand that Fujitsu, the creator, and
OL,11,Fmaintainer of Horizon, was altering
OL,12,Fbranch accounts.
OL,14,FHowever, Second Sight said the Post
OL,15,FOffice "repeatedly refused" to
OL,16,Fconsider faults with the Horizon
OL,17,Fsystem.
