OL,6,FAn interim report produced by Mr
OL,7,FHenderson and Mr Warmington in July
OL,8,F2013, identified two bugs in the
OL,9,Fsystem that caused problems for 76
OL,10,Fbranches.
OL,12,FThe forensic accountants were sacked
OL,13,Fin 2015, and Mr Henderson said he
OL,14,Fbelieved they were dismissed because
OL,15,Fthey were "getting too close to the
OL,16,Ftruth".
