OL,3,CPost Office involved in 'possible
OL,4,Ccriminal conspiracy', investigator says
OL,6,FMr Henderson was quizzed about the
OL,7,Flegal department at the Post Office
OL,8,Fthat he encountered while conducting
OL,9,Fhis review.
OL,11,FHe described it as a "relatively
OL,12,Fsmall" team that "somewhat
OL,13,Fshambolically and haphazardly" focused
OL,14,Fon storing files in paper form as
OL,15,Fopposed to electronically.
OL,17,FMr Henderson added that when he first
OL,18,Fstarted his work there were only "10
OL,19,For 12 legal case files available to
OL,20,Fme".
