OL,3,CPost Office involved in 'possible
OL,4,Ccriminal conspiracy', investigator says
OL,6,FLead Counsel to the inquiry Jason Beer
OL,7,FKC also probed Mr Henderson on his
OL,8,Fassessment of former Post Office
OL,9,Flawyer Jarnail Singh - who became head
OL,10,Fof criminal law in 2012 after the firm
OL,11,Fsplit with Royal Mail.
OL,13,FMr Henderson said that Mr Singh
OL,14,F"didn't strike me as a lawyer",
OL,15,Fadding: "He struck me more as an
OL,16,Fadministrator that was dealing with
OL,17,Ffarming out of potential cases,
OL,18,Fdealing with administrative matters,
OL,19,Fchasing progress by third-party
OL,20,Fsolicitors around the country.
