OL,4,Ccriminal conspiracy', investigator says
OL,6,F"His level of knowledge of
OL,7,Fprosecutions actually in my mind
OL,8,Fseemed to be quite limited."
OL,10,FSecret recordings obtained by ITV News
OL,11,Fearlier this year revealed proof of Mr
OL,12,FWarmington and Mr Henderson telling
OL,13,Fsenior Post Office bosses about their
OL,14,Fconcerns over the Horizon system.
OL,16,FOne recording was of a meeting held
OL,17,Fbetween the Post Office's top lawyer
OL,18,FChris Aujard and the two accountants
OL,19,Fin December 2013.
